OL,3,CDelays to Hillsborough Law
OL,4,C'extraordinary', writer Jimmy McGovern
OL,5,Csays
OL,7,FThe writer of a docudrama about the
OL,8,FHillsborough disaster says delays to
OL,9,Fthe introduction of a new law are
OL,10,F"extraordinary".
OL,12,FLiverpool-born writer Jimmy McGovern,
OL,13,Fwhose Bafta-winning 1996 drama
OL,14,FHillsborough drew attention to the
OL,15,Ffamilies' fight for justice, said he
OL,16,Fhad been following the progress of
OL,17,Flegislation for Hillsborough Law,
OL,18,Fwhich would include a duty for public
OL,19,Fbodies to tell the truth in the
OL,20,Faftermath of major disasters, as well
OL,21,Fas legal aid for families.
