OL,3,CDelays to Hillsborough Law
OL,4,C'extraordinary', writer Jimmy McGovern
OL,5,Csays
OL,7,FPrime Minister Sir Keir Starmer had
OL,8,Fpledged to bring in the law by the
OL,9,F36th anniversary of the tragedy, which
OL,10,Fwas on 15 April, but Downing Street
OL,11,Fsaid more time was needed to redraft
OL,12,Fit, amid fears it had been watered
OL,13,Fdown and would not include a legal
OL,14,Fduty of candour.
OL,16,FMcGovern said: "I just think it's
OL,17,Fextraordinary. What's going on there
OL,18,Fis people are demanding the right to
OL,19,Flie.
OL,21,F"That's what it's all about.
