OL,3,CDelays to Hillsborough Law
OL,4,C'extraordinary', writer Jimmy McGovern
OL,5,Csays
OL,7,F"They don't want a law that will tell
OL,8,Fpublic officials that they must tell
OL,9,Fthe truth.
OL,11,F"It killed 97 people, Hillsborough,
OL,12,Fand so they are demanding the right to
OL,13,Flie over another Hillsborough. 'We
OL,14,Fdemand the right to lie again'.
OL,15,FExtraordinary."
OL,17,FAn attempt by Liverpool West Derby MP
OL,18,FIan Byrne to introduce the Bill was
OL,19,Fblocked in the House of Commons
OL,20,Fearlier this month.
