OL,3,CDelays to Hillsborough Law
OL,4,C'extraordinary', writer Jimmy McGovern
OL,5,Csays
OL,7,FMcGovern's drama told the story of the
OL,8,Ftragedy at the FA Cup semi-final
OL,9,Fbetween Liverpool FC and Nottingham
OL,10,FForest at Hillsborough Stadium in
OL,11,FSheffield, in which 97 men, women and
OL,12,Fchildren died, and examined the build-
OL,13,Fup and aftermath.
OL,15,FIt has been credited as a key part in
OL,16,Fthe families' fight for justice, which
OL,17,Fsaw original inquest verdicts
OL,18,Foverturned and new inquests which
OL,19,Ffound that the victims were unlawfully
OL,20,Fkilled.
