OL,3,CDelays to Hillsborough Law
OL,4,C'extraordinary', writer Jimmy McGovern
OL,5,Csays
OL,7,FMcGovern said his work did not change
OL,8,Fanything, apart from the agenda.
OL,10,FHe said: "The change was all brought
OL,11,Fabout by the sheer determination of
OL,12,Fthe Hillsborough families.
OL,14,F"But I take great pleasure in the fact
OL,15,Fthat my docudrama did change the
OL,16,Fagenda for a short time."
OL,18,FHe said writing drama offered the
OL,19,Fopportunity to give a different
OL,20,Fperspective on an issue.
