OL,3,CDelays to Hillsborough Law
OL,4,C'extraordinary', writer Jimmy McGovern
OL,5,Csays
OL,7,F"That's why the powers that be are
OL,8,Falways sniffy about docudrama, because
OL,9,Fthe camera goes to the places where
OL,10,Fthey don't want it to go," he said.
OL,12,FThe writer said he was in a Manchester
OL,13,Fpub in 1982 when news came through
OL,14,Fthat Argentine Navy cruiser the ARA
OL,15,FGeneral Belgrano had been sunk by the
OL,16,FBritish during the Falklands War.
OL,18,FHe said: "People in the pub stood up
OL,19,Fand cheered.
