OL,3,CDelays to Hillsborough Law
OL,4,C'extraordinary', writer Jimmy McGovern
OL,5,Csays
OL,7,F"And I said to myself, they should be
OL,8,Fon that ship. They should see what
OL,9,Fit's like.
OL,11,F"Well, the camera can do that. The
OL,12,Fcamera fights against that kind of
OL,13,Fcheap, easy, bloodthirsty reaction."
OL,15,FMcGovern's new drama, Unforgivable,
OL,16,Fairs on BBC Two at 9pm on Thursday 24
OL,17,FJuly.
